      "author": "basdebruin (Bas de Bruin)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/vics\">@Vics</a></p>\n<p>Welcome to the community! When you want to update a board_relation (connect_boards) column you have to pass an array of itemIds you want to connect to. See <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/docs/connect#updating-the-connect-boards-column\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Connect boards</a> (section updating). Also: take note of this warning on that page.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/c/cc0365318e1d0462084972827b85265f011abc0c.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/c/cc0365318e1d0462084972827b85265f011abc0c.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"164\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">916×219 20.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
